{"title_page": "Sa\u00eff Ghezal", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2014}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Sa\u00eff Ghezal\n| image= Sa\u00eff Ghezal - Lausanne Sport vs. FC Thun - 22.10.2011.jpg\n| image_size = 220px\n| fullname = Sa\u00eff Ghezal\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1981|6|30|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[M'saken]], Tunisia\n| height = 1.90 m\n| currentclub  = [[ES Beni-Khalled|Beni-Khalled]] (Manager)\n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = \n| years1 = 2001\u20132008\n| years2 = 2008\u20132009\n| years3 = 2010\n| years4 = 2010\u20132011\n| years5 = 2011\u20132013\n| years6 = 2013\u20132014\n| clubs1 = [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]]\n| clubs2 = [[BSC Young Boys|Young Boys]]\n| clubs3 = [[Al-Ahli (Jeddah)|Ahli Jeddah]]\n| clubs4 = [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]]\n| clubs5 = [[FC Thun]]\n| clubs6 = [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]]\n| caps1 = 217\n| caps2 = 62\n| caps3 = 4\n| caps4 = 35\n| caps5 = 42\n| caps6 = 25\n| goals1 = 11\n| goals2 = 9\n| goals3 = 0\n| goals4 = 1\n| goals5 = 1\n| goals6 = 2\n| nationalyears1 = 2004\u20132009\n| nationalteam1 = [[Tunisia national football team|Tunisia]]\n| nationalcaps1 = 19\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| pcupdate = \n| ntupdate = \n| manageryears1 = 2017\n| managerclubs1 = [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]] (assistant)\n| manageryears2 = 2018\u20132019\n| managerclubs2 = [[ES Hammam-Sousse|Hammam-Sousse]]\n| manageryears3 = 2019\n| managerclubs3 = AS Rejiche\n| manageryears4 = 2019\n| managerclubs4 = [[Stade Sportif Sfaxien|SS Sfaxien]]\n| manageryears5 = 2020\u2013\n| managerclubs5 = [[ES Beni-Khalled|Beni-Khalled]]\n}}\n\n'''Sa\u00eff Ghezal''' ({{lang-ar|\u0633\u064a\u0641 \u063a\u0632\u0627\u0644}}; born 30 June 1981 in [[M'saken]]) is a retired [[Tunisia]]n [[Association football|footballer]] and current manager of [[ES Beni-Khalled]].\n\n==Career==\nGhezal previously played for [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel]], and participated at the [[2007 FIFA Club World Cup]].<ref name=\"FIFA\">{{FIFA player|213380|Sa\u00eff Ghezal}}</ref> He joined than in summer 2008 from [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel]] to Swiss club [[BSC Young Boys]]<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Guardian.co.uk|title=Sa\u00eff Ghezal: Facts|url=http://guardian.touch-line.com/StatsCentre.asp?Lang=0&CTID=25&CPID=99&pStr=Player&PLID=207242&TEID=1016|accessdate=17 December 2008}}</ref> and than left Ghezal his club to sign for [[Al-Ahli (Jeddah)|Al-Ahli Jeddah]] on 29 December 2009.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bernerzeitung.ch/sport/fussball/Der-raetselhafte-Abgang-von-Ghezal/story/23406651|title=Der r\u00e4tselhafte Abgang von Ghezal|work=Berner Zeitung, Berner Zeitung|access-date=2018-05-22|language=de|issn=1424-1021}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nGhezal has played for the senior [[Tunisia national football team]] during [[2010 FIFA World Cup qualification (CAF)|qualifying matches]] for the [[2010 FIFA World Cup]].<ref name=\"FIFA\" />\n\n==Coaching career==\nOn 5 February 2020, Ghezal was appointed manager of [[ES Beni-Khalled]].<ref>[http://alchourouk.com/article/%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%80%D9%81-%D8%BA%D9%80%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%85%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%D9%80%D8%A7-%D9%84%D9%84%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%80%D9%80%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AE%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A \u0633\u064a\u0640\u0641 \u063a\u0640\u0632\u0627\u0644 \u0645\u062f\u0631\u0628\u0640\u0627 \u0644\u0644\u0646\u062c\u0640\u0640\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0640\u0640\u0640\u0644\u0627\u062f\u064a], alchourouk.com, 5 February 2020</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{NFT player|7685}}\n* {{Webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090614013814/http://www.bscyb.ch/yb-mannschaft/yb-mann-pop-ghezal.htm |title=BSC Young Boys profile }} {{in lang|de}}\n* [http://www.football.ch/sfl/777842/de/Kader.aspx?tId=0&pId=764208 football.ch profile] {{dead link|date=April 2020}} {{in lang|de}}\n* {{FootballDatabase.eu|20581<!-- -saif-ghezal -->}}\n\n{{Tunisia squad 2008 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ghezal, Saif}}\n[[Category:1981 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Tunisian footballers]]\n[[Category:Tunisian football managers]]\n[[Category:Tunisia international footballers]]\n[[Category:2008 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel players]]\n[[Category:Al-Ahli Saudi FC players]]\n[[Category:BSC Young Boys players]]\n[[Category:FC Thun players]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Swiss Super League players]]\n[[Category:Tunisian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Switzerland]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Saudi Arabia]]\n[[Category:Tunisian expatriate sportspeople in Saudi Arabia]]\n[[Category:Saudi Professional League players]]\n[[Category:Mediterranean Games gold medalists for Tunisia]]\n[[Category:Mediterranean Games medalists in football]]\n[[Category:Competitors at the 2001 Mediterranean Games]]\n[[Category:ES Hammam-Sousse managers]]\n\n\n{{Tunisia-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2014}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Sa\u00eff Ghezal\n| image= Sa\u00eff Ghezal - Lausanne Sport vs. FC Thun - 22.10.2011.jpg\n| image_size = 220px\n| fullname = Sa\u00eff Ghezal\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1981|6|30|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[M'saken]], Tunisia\n| height = {{convert|1.90|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}\n| currentclub  = [[ES Beni-Khalled|Beni-Khalled]] (Manager)\n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| youthyears1 =   \n| youthclubs1 =   \n| years1 = 2001\u20132008 \n| years2 = 2008\u20132009 \n| years3 = 2010 \n| years4 = 2010\u20132011\n| years5 = 2011\u20132013\n| years6 = 2013\u20132014\n| clubs1 = [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]] \n| clubs2 = [[BSC Young Boys|Young Boys]] \n| clubs3 = [[Al-Ahli (Jeddah)|Ahli Jeddah]] \n| clubs4 = [[\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel|ES Sahel]]\