ia national football team]] during [[2010 FIFA World Cup qualification (CAF)|qualifying matches]] for the [[2010 FIFA World Cup]].<ref name=\"FIFA\" />\n\n==Coaching career==\nOn 5 February 2020, Ghezal was appointed manager of [[ES Beni-Khalled]].<ref>[http://alchourouk.com/article/%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%80%D9%81-%D8%BA%D9%80%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%84-%D9%85%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A8%D9%80%D8%A7-%D9%84%D9%84%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%80%D9%80%D9%85-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AE%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%8A \u0633\u064a\u0640\u0641 \u063a\u0640\u0632\u0627\u0644 \u0645\u062f\u0631\u0628\u0640\u0627 \u0644\u0644\u0646\u062c\u0640\u0640\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u062e\u0640\u0640\u0640\u0644\u0627\u062f\u064a], alchourouk.com, 5 February 2020</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{NFT player|pid=7685}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090614013814/http://www.bscyb.ch/yb-mannschaft/yb-mann-pop-ghezal.htm BSC Young Boys profile] {{in lang|de}}\n* [http://www.football.ch/sfl/777842/de/Kader.aspx?tId=0&pId=764208 football.ch profile] {{in lang|de}}\n* {{FootballDatabase.eu|20581-saif-ghezal}}\n\n{{Tunisia squad 2008 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ghezal, Saif}}\n[[Category:1981 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Tunisian footballers]]\n[[Category:Tunisian football managers]]\n[[Category:Tunisia international footballers]]\n[[Category:2008 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:\u00c9toile Sportive du Sahel players]]\n[[Category:Al-Ahli Saudi FC players]]\n[[Category:BSC Young Boys players]]\n[[Category:FC Thun players]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Swiss Super League players]]\n[[Category:Tunisian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Switzerland]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Saudi Arabia]]\n[[Category:Tunisian expatriate sportspeople in Saudi Arabia]]\n[[Category:Saudi Professional League players]]\n[[Category:Mediterranean Games gold medalists for Tunisia]]\n[[Category:Mediterranean Games med